snippet.title: Attack On Titan 2: Final Battle  - Official Stadia Reveal Trailer | Gamescom 2019
snippet.description: The stakes have never been higher as an all-out battle for the fate of humanity is about to begin. Can Eren and the Scouts overcome overwhelming odds and take down the Beast Titan, Amored Titan and more? Join the fight when Attack on Titan 2: Final Battle comes to Stadia.
